'''[[absorption]] [[line]]'''
#{{physics}},{{astronomy}} a dark line in a [[continuous]] [[spectrum]] that corresponds to the absorption of [[electromagnetic radiation]] at a specific [[wavelength]]; the [[pattern]] of such lines is characteristic of specific [[atom]]s or [[molecule]]s in the path of the radiation

